StructureDefinition-qcvs

source file: source/pages/_includes/qcvs-intro.md

The Argonaut Questionnaire Contained ValueSet Profile is contained within the Argonaut Questionnaire Profile:

  • ​It requires an expansion of the code set to constrains the concepts to particular set of conditions for a given questionnaire.

  • ​The Ordinal Value extension is added as a Must Support element to support the calculation of scores from the associated assessments.

  • The ValueSet.url element is constrained to a Must Support element to provide an alternative literal address at which this value set is (or will be) published.
